{"tid":1828534,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"第一階段貿易協議後人仔匯價走勢討論","createTime":"2020-01-18T02:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T09:34:46.000Z","uid":264908,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c5f5a1fc843599634c0deaa540cb6ca8c6238da5","tid":1828534,"uid":264908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T02:55:28.000Z","msg":"貿戰開波前近幾年花旗國流失的工作職位同美元數以千億計，為咗追返呢筆數，咁侵侵係咪有誘因優先考慮唔好咁快畀人仔狂跌，必要時喺唔使美國再出真金白銀下，出手幫托人仔，令人仔貶值速度減慢甚至牛皮企硬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffad70f8d53ac65c9e2a7a436d9f0c18c8c8e07","tid":1828534,"uid":138588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T02:58:07.000Z","msg":"點解貶值？<br />\n理論上係升值喎"},{"pid":"c63456692f964757f8600f0a0957099686b6567c","tid":1828534,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T02:59:32.000Z","msg":"啲債到期先會跌<br />\n<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"418d7e143f2b042dccce09271ccbf043de439164","tid":1828534,"uid":264908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ffad70f8d53ac65c9e2a7a436d9f0c18c8c8e07","tid":1828534,"uid":138588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T02:58:07.000Z","msg":"點解貶值？<br />\n理論上係升值喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T03:06:01.000Z","msg":"要用返美元去買美國貨找數，咁儲備中嘅美元咪減少囉。<br />\n仲要而家出口去美國嘅貨要收關稅，美元外匯收入大減。<br />\n中共國荷包美元儲備一邊大失血，一邊無輸血，咁人仔無外匯儲備支撐同經濟收縮，就梗係走貶。"},{"pid":"8446d0d62d4bdfc0a569b24e3341f799ead028b5","tid":1828534,"uid":55445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T03:06:32.000Z","msg":"美帝實谷佢升<br />\n支那唔想升<br />\n應該橫行<br />\n如果跌美帝實反台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03fe100ad49ce72e6e76b481d06676ddabb150c7","tid":1828534,"uid":264908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8446d0d62d4bdfc0a569b24e3341f799ead028b5","tid":1828534,"uid":55445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T03:06:32.000Z","msg":"美帝實谷佢升<br />\n支那唔想升<br />\n應該橫行<br />\n如果跌美帝實反台<i